		<title>7 AI Marketing Trends for 2024 &#038; What They Mean for You</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-marketing-trends-2024</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[John Shieldsmith]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 12:30:07 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence (AI)]]></category>
